Scroll through the pics and you will also see that he was senior prom king this year as well! SO PROUD OF YOU MY COLLEGE BOUND NEPHEW!!
Happy PRIDE to all! 🏳️‍🌈 I SEE you, I HEAR you, I SUPPORT you!
